"widgetAddChild(icon, ImageSymbol(\"bell\"))\n"
"const dotBadge = Text(\"3\")\n"
"widgetAddOverlay(icon, dotBadge)\n"
"widgetSetOverlayFrame(dotBadge, 20, -5, 16, 16)\n"
"```"
